creator: Evaneos
descriptionHtml:
The travel companion connecting you with your local agent.

STAY IN TOUCH WITH YOUR LOCAL AGENT
Discuss and organize your trip with a local agent directly from your phone. Send messages, images, and files whenever you need to. Receive notifications for each new message or alert from your agent, ensuring a smooth planning experience and an incredible adventure. The best way of organizing the perfect trip made just for you.

ALL YOU NEED TO KNOW ABOUT YOUR TRIP
Log into the app and get all the info on your trip from anywhere: dates, location, agent contact and much more, all right in your pocket.
Have a problem while traveling? Get in direct contact with your local agent to ensure a safe and relaxing trip.

YOUR DESTINATION GUIDE
The best places to visit, what to bring, and whatever you need to know...The answer to every question about your destination is available on the app.

MUCH MORE TO COME
This version is only the first step, much more will be added in the following months to make the Evaneos app an even smarter travel companion. Stay tuned.

Don’t have an account yet? Discover Evaneos by visiting our website: evaneos.com

creator: Evaneos
descriptionHtml:
The travel companion connecting you with your local agent.

STAY IN TOUCH WITH YOUR LOCAL AGENT
Discuss and organize your trip with a local agent directly from your phone. Send messages, images, and files whenever you need to. Receive notifications for each new message or alert from your agent, ensuring a smooth planning experience and an incredible adventure. The best way of organizing the perfect trip made just for you.

ALL YOU NEED TO KNOW ABOUT YOUR TRIP
Log into the app and get all the info on your trip from anywhere: dates, location, agent contact and much more, all right in your pocket.
Have a problem while traveling? Get in direct contact with your local agent to ensure a safe and relaxing trip.

YOUR DESTINATION GUIDE
The best places to visit, what to bring, and whatever you need to know...The answer to every question about your destination is available on the app.

MUCH MORE TO COME
This version is only the first step, much more will be added in the following months to make the Evaneos app an even smarter travel companion. Stay tuned.

Don’t have an account yet? Discover Evaneos by visiting our website: evaneos.com
